Files: libisc/*
Copyright: 1999-2003 Internet Software Consortium
           2004-2015 Internet Systems Consortium, Inc. ("ISC")
           2015 NTPsec project contributors
Comment: This is not compatible with upstream libisc. The NTPsec lead developer
         says they have made changes to the API.  Here is their comment, from
         libisc/README:
           The code in this directory derives from an old version (91) of
           the ISC export library shipped with BIND9.  Most of the code in that
           library was not needed and has been discarded.
