Files: libjsmn/*
Copyright: 2012-2015 Serge Zaitsev <zaitsev.serge@gmail.com>
Comment: This is currently used.  The plan is to create a standalone package of
         libjsmn (from the upstream sources).  Then, this package would build
         against that. Note that several other packages in Debian (including
         ntp) currently embed libjsmn.  They could also be fixed to use the
         standalone libjsmn package once it is created.
